# Course Builder Project Rules (SegFormer Focus)

## Python Environment
- Virtualenv at project root: `.venv`
- Use `.venv/bin/python` and `.venv/bin/pip` from project root.
- Tests: `cd /home/ubuntu/github/jmjava/course-builder && .venv/bin/pytest`

## Project Structure
- `phase1_1/` – SegFormer training (Danish Golf Courses), inference, masks → polygons → SVG
- `phase1a/` – Interactive tracing (SegFormer + SAM), hole assignment, SVG export
- `archive/` – Phase 1, old ROADMAP, workspace (inactive)

## Testing
- phase1a: `.venv/bin/pytest phase1a/tests/ -v`
- Skip GUI: `--ignore=phase1a/tests/test_gui_integration.py`
- phase1_1: `.venv/bin/pytest phase1_1/tests/ -v` (when present)

## SVG Output
- Match `phase1a/resources/RockRidge_No_Overlay.svg`: inline `opacity:0.5;fill:#XXXXXX`, `inkscape:label`, layer groups `inkscape:groupmode="layer"` / `inkscape:label="HoleN"`.
